quran[29]{c,v,t}:
  37,154,"at is the matter with you? How (arbitrarily) do you judge?"
  37,155,"Then, is it that you do not think about it?"
  37,156,"Or, is it that there is some open authority with you?"
  37,157,"Then bring your book, if you are truthful."
  37,158,"And they have made up between Him and the Jinns some kinship, while the Jinns already know that they are bound to appear (before Him)."
  37,159,"Pure is Allah from what they describe -"
  37,160,"except the chosen servants of Allah."
  37,161,"So, you and those whom you worship -"
  37,162,"none of you can make one turn away from Him -"
  37,163,"except the one who is to burn in Jahannam."
  37,164,"And (the angels say,) "There is no one among us who does not have a known station,"
  37,165,"and We, surely We, are those who stand in rows"
  37,166,"and We, surely We, are those who proclaim Allah's purity.""
  37,167,"And they used to say,"
  37,168,""Had there been a scripture like that of the former ones with us,"
  37,169,"certainly we would have been the chosen servants of Allah.""
  37,170,"Then they disbelieved in it. So, very soon, they will come to know."
  37,171,"And Our Word has already gone ahead in favor of Our servants - the messengers -"
  37,172,"they are the ones who will have Allah's support,"
  37,173,"and verily it will be Our army (of chosen servants) that prevails."
  37,174,"So, withdraw your attention from them for a time."
  37,175,"But, see them for they shall soon see."
  37,176,"Are they asking for Our punishment to come sooner?"
  37,177,"So, when it descends in their courtyard, then, evil will be the dawn of those warned."
  37,178,"So, withdraw your attention from them for a time."
  37,179,"And watch them, for they shall soon see."
  37,180,"Pure is your Lord, the Lord of all might and honor, from what they describe"
  37,181,"and salam be on the messengers"
  37,182,"and praised is Allah, Lord of all the worlds."